{"tid":2451581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改選舉制度、削弱鄉士派、打擊套丁網絡，政府土地改革第一步？","createTime":"2021-03-18T08:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T09:00:24.000Z","uid":273675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc19f33f226e4f1943c5e5112e935a426043eea","tid":2451581,"uid":273675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"在全國兩會舉行期間，國務院副總理韓正曾參加港區全國人大小組會議，明言中央將處理香港貧富懸殊及房屋問題。既然要著手解決住屋問題，在地少人多的香港，那地從何來呢？一直以來引起爭議的棕地發展，到底又遇到甚麼阻力？<br />\n<br />\n近日，在中央政府提倡的新選舉制度下，鄉議局被納入地區組織界別；同時更有廉署「芒草」行動，大舉拘捕了套丁利益網絡。到底，這是否意味政府可更有效進行土地改革、解決香港房屋問題呢？<br />\n#韓正 #貧富懸殊 #土地改革 #棕地發展 #鄉事委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100154268032623/posts/483332293048150/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100154268032623%2Fposts%2F483332293048150%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2XwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=2874f0c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100154268032623/posts/483332293048150/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJK574d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJK574d.png&h=8f1f1907&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mQUgXz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mQUgXz.png&h=a33c5468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXjBvhz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXjBvhz.png&h=2b4ff58c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNL85QV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNL85QV.png&h=886afe23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2JPqoCA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2JPqoCA.png&h=c45abe21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4ye1pg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4ye1pg.png&h=65bba80e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XsWvhB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.